<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Panel de administrador | Iglesia Solidaria</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a2d0b1fac5.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-[var(--bg-soft)] text-color1 font-sans">
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-[var(--border-soft)] bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <a href="index.html" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-color1">Iglesia Solidaria</a>
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-color2">
        <a href="index.html" class="nav-link rounded-full px-4 py-2">Inicio</a>
        <a href="donate.html" class="nav-link rounded-full px-4 py-2">Donar</a>
        <a href="index.html#contact" class="nav-link rounded-full px-4 py-2">Contacto</a>
        <span id="adminUserBadge" class="adminUserBadge"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i> <span id="adminUserName">admin</span></span>
        <button type="button" id="adminLogoutButton" class="adminAccessBtn">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i> Salir
        </button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl space-y-8 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <section class="donationHeroPanel overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-[var(--border-soft)] bg-white/85 shadow-[0_24px_80px_rgba(82,46,39,0.08)] backdrop-blur-md">
      <div class="p-7 sm:p-10">
        <p class="sectionEyebrow">Panel de control</p>
        <h1 class="sectionTitle mt-4 text-[2.2rem]">Donaciones recibidas</h1>
        <p class="sectionLead mt-4">Revisa cada aporte, confirma quién lo hizo y decide si se aprueba o se rechaza. Los cambios se reflejan al instante en los totales del sitio.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="metricCard">
            <span>Total de donaciones</span>
            <strong id="statTotalCount">0</strong>
            <p>Registros recibidos hasta ahora.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metricCard">
            <span>Pendientes</span>
            <strong id="statPendingCount">0</strong>
            <p>Esperando revisión del administrador.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metricCard">
            <span>Aprobadas</span>
            <strong id="statApprovedCount">0</strong>
            <p>Confirmadas y contadas en el total.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metricCard">
            <span>Recaudado vigente</span>
            <strong id="statTotalAmount">$0</strong>
            <p>Suma de causas, sin lo rechazado.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[2rem] border border-[var(--border-soft)] bg-white p-7 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(82,46,39,0.08)] sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" id="statusFilterGroup">
          <button type="button" class="filterTab is-active" data-filter="todas">Todas</button>
          <button type="button" class="filterTab" data-filter="pendiente">Pendientes</button>
          <button type="button" class="filterTab" data-filter="aprobada">Aprobadas</button>
          <button type="button" class="filterTab" data-filter="rechazada">Rechazadas</button>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full max-w-xs">
          <input id="donationSearchInput" type="text" placeholder="Buscar por nombre de donante..." class="modernInput w-full" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <p id="adminActionFeedback" class="mt-4 min-h-[1.5rem] text-sm text-[#2c7a2a]"></p>

      <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="donationsTable w-full">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Donante</th>
              <th>Causa</th>
              <th>Monto</th>
              <th>Tarjeta</th>
              <th>Fecha</th>
              <th>Estado</th>
              <th>Acciones</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="donationsTableBody"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p id="emptyStateMessage" class="mt-6 hidden text-center text-sm text-color3">No hay donaciones que coincidan con este filtro.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="js/store.js"></script>
  <script src="js/admin.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
